LilycoveCity_DepartmentStore_4F_Text_AttackOrDefenseTM:
	.string "Hmm…\p"
	.string "An attacking move…\n"
	.string "Or a defensive move…\p"
	.string "It's no easy matter to decide which TM\n"
	.string "moves should be taught to POKéMON…$"

LilycoveCity_DepartmentStore_4F_Text_FiftyDifferentTMs:
	.string "There are so many different kinds of\n"
	.string "TM moves.\p"
	.string "A catalog I read said there are 100\n"
	.string "different kinds.$"

LilycoveCity_DepartmentStore_4F_Text_PokemonOnlyHaveFourMoves:
	.string "I'd like to get all the different TMs,\n"
	.string "but a POKéMON learns only four moves.$"

`

text LilycoveCity_DepartmentStore_4F_Text_EvoItems{
    "Welcome!\p
    I sell a bunch of EVOLUTION items!"
}

text LilycoveCity_DepartmentStore_4F_Text_WeatherItems{
    "Welcome!\p
    Get your field setting items here!"
}

text LilycoveCity_DepartmentStore_4F_Text_HoldItems{
    "Welcome, welcome!\p
    I got MUST-HAVE hold items for sale!\n
    Guaranteed to upgrade your battling!"
}

text LilycoveCity_DepartmentStore_4F_Text_TMs{
    "TMs! Get your TMs here!\n
    We have tons of rare TMs!"
}
